# Shared Index — {{MODULE_NAME}}

<!--
  This file is the module's view of the parent's shared assets. It lists every parent-
  shared file the module has permission to read, the relative path from this module
  folder, and the snapshot state at last sync.

  CRITICAL RULES:
    1. This file is an INDEX, not a cache. Parent assets are referenced via relative
       path and read live — they are NOT copied into the module folder.
    2. Only sync (or parent setup Step 7g) writes this file. The module session reads
       from it. The module session never edits it directly.
    3. Each entry has a `last_seen_hash` recorded at the last sync. If the parent file
       changes, the next sync will flag it as `drift: true` until the user acknowledges.
    4. Overrides (per-module shared-asset variants) are marked explicitly with an
       `← OVERRIDE` annotation and the path to the local replacement file.

  Full model: references/parent-module-handoff.md §shared-assets-access
  Conflicts: references/conflict-resolution.md §shared-asset-edits
-->

